(111, 1, '2010-07-11 14:37:48', '2010-07-11 14:37:48', '<a href="http://www.shropgeek-revolution.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/IMG_0482.jpg"><img src="http://www.shropgeek-revolution.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/IMG_0482-225x300.jpg" alt="Shropgeek" title="Shropgeek" width="225" height="300" class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-141" /></a>Shropgeek was originally started 18 months ago by Zach Beauvais and Dean (Leu) Thorne, The idea was simple. A ''tweetup'' once a month for like-minded geeks from around Shropshire. The definition of a geek was always meant to be a loose one, welcoming anyone with that spark of the hacker about them: from developers and designers to enthusiasts and creative-types. It was meant to be an experiment to see how many fellow geks there were, and the results were surprising!\n\nSadly Leu passed away on 18<sup>th</sup> September 2009. However, after a break, a fellow regular Kirsty Burgoine stepped in to help organize the tweetups.\n\nMostly publicized through twitter, Shropgeek meet ups are held on the 1st Friday of every month at the Admiral Benbow in Shrewsbury. The evenings start at 7.30pm and are a great opportunity for people working in all industries to socialize with no pressure of networking.\n\nEach month people from all areas of the IT industry get together and enjoy a relaxed evening of beer and chat. There are no speeches or sales pitches, just like minded individuals sitting in a pub discussing the current events within the IT and web industries.\n\nThe next three monthly meet ups will be:\n\nFriday 6th August 2010\nFriday 3rd September 2010\nFriday 1st October 2010\n\n<strong>Anybody is welcome to come along. The only criteria for joining in with Shropgeek is you have to show up!</strong>\n\nYou can find out a bit more information and see reviews of previous meetups by visiting the website: <a href="http://www.shropgeek.co.uk" target="_blank">www.shropgeek.co.uk</a>\n\nAlternatively, you can follow us on twitter: <a href="http://www.twitter.com/shropgeek" target="_blank">@shropgeek</a>', 'About Shropgeek', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-autosave', '', '', '2010-07-11 14:37:48', '2010-07-11 14:37:48', '', 2, 'http://www.shropgeek-revolution.co.uk/uncategorized/2-autosave', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(112, 1, '2010-07-07 23:51:37', '2010-07-07 23:51:37', 'This is an example of a WordPress page, you could edit this to put information about yourself or your site so readers know where you are coming from. You can create as many pages like this one or sub-pages as you like and manage all of your content inside of WordPress.', 'About Shropgeek', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-4', '', '', '2010-07-07 23:51:37', '2010-07-07 23:51:37', '', 2, 'http://www.shropgeek-revolution.co.uk/uncategorized/2-revision-4', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
